Interface ClaimableHolder

All Known Subinterfaces:
Aggregation, Allocation, AllocationforCollections, AssetTransfer, Disposition, Expansion, NewExpansion, NewPlanElement, PEforCollections, PlanElement, PlanElementForAssessor
All Known Implementing Classes:
AggregationImpl, AllocationImpl, AssetTransferImpl, DispositionImpl, ExpansionImpl, PlanElementImpl
public interface ClaimableHolder

An indirect holder of a Claimable.

Claiming of objects is done by the infrastruture *only* - plugins should *never* call "getClaimable().claim()".
